64
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:20,460
Grandpa's old stuff is in the study.

65
00:03:20,460 --> 00:03:21,600
Let's go check it.

66
00:03:25,860 --> 00:03:26,700
Here we go.

67
00:03:28,260 --> 00:03:29,220
